metadata.name: Dohora
metadata.description:
This is Dochora, one of the supreme goddesses living on the planet Venus. Her great power given to her by her ancient ancestors lies in her ability to control water. 

All her thoughts are pure and transparent, but in her rage she can sweep away anything, like a raging hurricane of 12 points...

She loves her planet very much and has stood up for it more than once. But now she enjoys peace on the banks of the Venerian River...
